eted": 0, "content": "今天突然發現自帶的輸入法輸入變成了繁體，就去 Google 搜索下載搜狗輸入法，結果前三排竟然都是同一個野鷄網站\r\nhttps://s.wdfeff.club/， 做的和官網還一模一樣，下載下來的程序沒有簽名，估計是什麽木馬病毒。\r\n\r\n這是搜索結果排名的圖片，可沒冤枉 Google ，他還貼心的給你標注是贊助商廣告。\r\nhttps://imgur.com/a/fownNfu\r\n\r\n能理解打廣告，但你好歹把官網放在第一排啊，誰給的錢多就把誰放第一個，這和百度有什麽區別，Google 早點死吧。", "content_rendered": "<p>今天突然發現自帶的輸入法輸入變成了繁體，就去 Google 搜索下載搜狗輸入法，結果前三排竟然都是同一個野鷄網站\n<a href=\"https://s.wdfeff.club/%EF%BC%8C\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://s.wdfeff.club/，</a> 做的和官網還一模一樣，下載下來的程序沒有簽名，估計是什麽木馬病毒。</p>\n<p>這是搜索結果排名的圖片，可沒冤枉 Google ，他還貼心的給你標注是贊助商廣告。\n<a href=\"https://imgur.com/a/fownNfu\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://imgur.com/a/fownNfu</a></p>\n<p>能理解打廣告，但你好歹把官網放在第一排啊，誰給的錢多就把誰放第一個，這和百度有什麽區別，Google 早點死吧。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1696646078, "replies": 62, "id": 979388}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc49/0ca4/65_large.png?m=1524891806", "name": "google", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc49/0ca4/65_normal.png?m=1524891806", "title": "Google", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/google", "topics": 3085, "footer": "", "header": "Google’s mission is to organize the world’s information and make it universally accessible and useful.", "title_alternative": "Google", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/fc49/0ca4/65_mini.png?m=1524891806", "stars": 3617, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 65, "parent_node_name": "internet"}, "member": {"id": 206459, "username": "xiaopanzi", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/xiaopanzi", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a2a3/d5b8/206459_mini.png?m=1683524953", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a2a3/d5b8/206459_normal.png?m=1683524953", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/a2a3/d5b8/206459_large.png?m=1683524953", "created": 1481970782, "last_modified": 1683524953}, "last_reply_by": "dif", "last_touched": 1696628946, "title": "Google voice 保号方案", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/979173", "created": 1696563764, "deleted": 0, "content": "我记得之前接收短信就能实现保号，但是现在它的通知邮件说：\r\n\r\n> If you’d like to keep your Google Voice number xxx, you will need to make calls or send text messages by November 4, 2023 by logging in to your account or using the Google Voice app on Android or iOS.\r\n\r\n是不是现在要主动发送短信或打电话才行？那么此时最方便的保号方案是什么？", "content_rendered": "<p>我记得之前接收短信就能实现保号，但是现在它的通知邮件说：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>If you’d like to keep your Google Voice number xxx, you will need to make calls or send text messages by November 4, 2023 by logging in to your account or using the Google Voice app on Android or iOS.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>是不是现在要主动发送短信或打电话才行？那么此时最方便的保号方案是什么？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1696563764, "replies": 57, "id": 979173}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_large.png?m=1651385965", "name": "android", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_normal.png?m=1651385965", "title": "Android", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/android", "topics": 10662, "footer": "", "header": "来自 <a href=\"/go/google\">Google</a> 的开放源代码智能手机平台。", "title_alternative": "Android", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/d67d/8ab4/39_mini.png?m=1651385965", "stars": 5541, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 39, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 150233, "username": "jjxtrotter", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/jjxtrotter", "website": "", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4a1ae1c5e0dc0471e75ca11348b9deff?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4a1ae1c5e0dc0471e75ca11348b9deff?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/4a1ae1c5e0dc0471e75ca11348b9deff?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1449413759, "last_modified": 1696602811}, "last_reply_by": "p1gd0g", "last_touched": 1696645932, "title": "进来试试你的设备支不支持真*HDR 图片", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/979304", "created": 1696603096, "deleted": 0, "content": "苹果生态下目前最新的 iOS/iPadOS/macOS 已经在原生照片.app 内支持.avif 等格式的真 HDR 照片（硬件支持的情况下）。我想看看 Android 端原生图片 app （不是浏览器）对 HDR 照片的支持情况，但是手头没有 Android 设备无法测试，想看看大家的测试结果，列出设备型号和系统版本。\r\n\r\n关于 HDR 照片，可以参考视频：[护城河苹果，重新定义 HDR]( https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1V14y1R7Rk/?vd_source=317847acc68968c9f3ec0ce5e34758c9)\r\n\r\n测试链接： https://people.csail.mit.edu/ericchan/hdr/hdr.php\r\n\r\n注意：本次测试的是手机默认图片/照片 app 对 HDR 图片的支持情况，不是浏览器，所以打开链接后请手动保存图片进入手机自带照片 app 查看。", "content_rendered": "<p>苹果生态下目前最新的 iOS/iPadOS/macOS 已经在原生照片.app 内支持.avif 等格式的真 HDR 照片（硬件支持的情况下）。我想看看 Android 端原生图片 app （不是浏览器）对 HDR 照片的支持情况，但是手头没有 Android 设备无法测试，想看看大家的测试结果，列出设备型号和系统版本。</p>\n<p>关于 HDR 照片，可以参考视频：<a href=\"https://www.bilibili.com/video/BV1V14y1R7Rk/?vd_source=317847acc68968c9f3ec0ce5e34758c9\" rel=\"nofollow\">护城河苹果，重新定义 HDR</a></p>\n<p>测试链接： <a href=\"https://people.csail.mit.edu/ericchan/hdr/hdr.php\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://people.csail.mit.edu/ericchan/hdr/hdr.php</a></p>\n<p>注意：本次测试的是手机默认图片/照片 app 对 HDR 图片的支持情况，不是浏览器，所以打开链接后请手动保存图片进入手机自带照片 app 查看。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1696603096, "replies": 49, "id": 979304}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913", "name": "apple", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913", "title": "Apple", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple", "topics": 23792, "footer": "", "header": "设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。", "title_alternative": "Apple", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913", "stars": 2738, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 184, "parent_node_name": "hardware"}, "member": {"id": 642014, "username": "RyanLens", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/RyanLens", "website": null, "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": null, "tagline": n