f?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1693717677, "last_modified": 1693717677}, "last_reply_by": "tanrenye", "last_touched": 1696646499, "title": "macOS Sonoma 用着怎么样？", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/979167", "created": 1696561953, "deleted": 0, "content": "Ventura 用着比较顺手比较稳，看 Sonoma 更新的内容有点提不起升级的兴趣。\r\n大家升级 Sonoma 的用着怎么样？和 Ventura 比呢？", "content_rendered": "<p>Ventura 用着比较顺手比较稳，看 Sonoma 更新的内容有点提不起升级的兴趣。\n大家升级 Sonoma 的用着怎么样？和 Ventura 比呢？</p>\n", "last_modified": 1696561953, "replies": 47, "id": 979167}]